A breathable mesh base pairs with sturdy overlays for support that stands up to school days and weekend adventures, while reflective hits add a subtle pop in low light. Underfoot, the 9060’s signature cushioning delivers plush step-in comfort tailored for all-day wear. A dual-density setup featuring ABZORB and SBS-inspired tech helps soften impact and maintain stability, and the exaggerated outsole lugs grip sidewalks, gym floors, and playground surfaces with ease. The padded collar and tongue create a snug, secure feel without bulk, and the GC9060BB build keeps weight balanced for easy transitions from class to play. With its modern proportions and timeless Triple Black finish, this kids’ 9060 turns everyday outfits into a statement while keeping feet supported and ready for anything.

Our team loves this product because it blends standout style with dependable cushioning and traction, making it a go-to kids’ sneaker for school, sport, and everywhere in between.

The crisp Swoosh pops against Game Royal, and thoughtful touches like the molded scales and streamlined proportions give this shoe a polished, modern feel. products.description:
The Air Jordan 4 Retro Flight Club GS channels classic Jordan energy through a colorway that feels bold, sporty, and rooted in basketball tradition. The sail base paired with black and university red accents gives the Jordan 4 a strong visual punch, highlighting its iconic shape and flight inspired details. It feels energetic and expressive, designed to stand out while staying true to the silhouette’s heritage.

Collectors gravitate toward this pair because it captures the spirit of Jordan Brand at its most dynamic. The Flight Club theme reinforces movement, confidence, and identity, making the shoe feel alive rather than static. Fans love it as a versatile Jordan 4 that balances statement making color with everyday wearability, keeping it relevant on the court and in rotation.

The Air Jordan 4 Retro Flight Club GS was released on January 17, 2026 with a retail price of $165.
products.name: Jordan 4 Retro Flight Club (GS)

products.description:
Nike Ja 3 Turbo Green GS brings high energy color to Ja Morant’s signature line in a way that feels youthful and fearless. Turbo Green injects brightness into the Ja 3, amplifying the sense of speed and movement that defines the silhouette. Even in grade school sizing, the shoe feels bold and expressive rather than simplified.

Collectors appreciate this pair because it mirrors Ja’s on court personality so clearly. The Ja 3 thrives on motion and aggression, and the Turbo Green colorway reinforces that identity with confidence. It feels fun and motivating, designed for fans who want performance footwear that carries attitude and excitement alongside function.

The Nike Ja 3 Turbo Green GS was released on 11/05/2025 with a retail price of $100.

products.description:
Air Jordan 12 Retro Pearl Pink GS brings a soft and playful twist to one of Jordan Brand’s most celebrated silhouettes, wrapping the classic Air Jordan 12 in tones that feel both premium and youthful. The pearl pink palette floods the tumbled leather upper, giving it a warm, elegant presence that still carries the performance inspired shape created by Tinker Hatfield. Even in grade school sizing, this release feels luxurious and intentional, perfect for collectors who appreciate subtle color stories rooted in heritage design.

Collectors gravitate toward the Pearl Pink because it marries iconic structure with refined personality. The Air Jordan 12’s signature radiating stitch lines and supportive build remain front and center, while the gentle pink hues create a fresh narrative that feels timeless rather than trend driven. It’s the kind of release that feels at home in curated rotations and everyday rotation alike.

The Air Jordan 12 Retro Pearl Pink GS was released on 11/21/2025 with a retail price of $150.
products.name: Jordan 12 Retro Pearl Pink (GS)

products.description:
The Air Jordan 4 Retro Midnight Navy GS applies color blocking in light smoke grey and midnight navy to dress the sneaker.
​
​This Retro Air Jordan 4 for grade-schoolers is available in a white/​midnight navy/​light smoke grey/​fire colorway. The upper is made of white leather with light grey support Wings, a matching light grey heel tab with Jumpman branding imprinted on top, and navy molded eyelets. The woven tongue tag has an additional Jumpman graphic in navy. The sneaker has a two-tone polyurethane midsole with encapsulated AIR in the forefoot and an exposed unit in the heel.
​
​The Air Jordan 4 Retro Midnight Navy GS was released on the 29th of October 2022, retailing for $160.
products.name: Jordan 4 Retro Midnight Navy (GS)

products.description:
The Jordan 12 Retro French Blue (2025) (GS) revives a fan-favorite colorway with crisp, confident style for everyday wear and standout moments. A smooth White leather upper sets the stage for the signature French Blue mudguard with its textured, pebbled finish, while Metallic Silver eyelets and Varsity Red Jumpman hits add sharp contrast. Inspired by luxury design cues and performance heritage, the AJ12’s sculpted lines and sunburst stitching deliver timeless appeal. Underfoot, a responsive setup supported by a carbon-fiber shank and durable herringbone traction keeps every step stable, whether on the move or on display. 

Built in grade school sizing for a dialed-in fit, this pair blends comfort and durability with court-bred details. The full-length cushioning typical of the 12 pairs with a supportive midsole to help soften landings and power quick cuts, while the rubber outsole grips across city streets and gym floors alike. A woven heel tab and "Two 3" embroidery on the tongue nod to heritage, and the classic blocking in White/French Blue/Metallic Silver/Varsity Red makes style ID 153265-114 an easy match for uniforms and weekend fits. With the 2025 release date, this is the refresh collectors have been waiting for, clean, versatile, and instantly recognizable.

Our team loves this product because it combines iconic Jordan DNA with all-day comfort and a bold French Blue pop that elevates any rotation.
products.name: Jordan 12 Retro French Blue (2025) (GS)

products.description:
The Nike Kobe 5 Year of the Mamba Eggplant (GS) is a striking tribute to the legendary Kobe Bryant, designed specifically for young athletes. This Grade School edition showcases a bold eggplant purple upper, accented with sleek black details and luxurious metallic gold accents. The shoe's design seamlessly blends style and performance, featuring Nike's innovative technologies to provide superior comfort and support on the court.

Engineered with the needs of growing athletes in mind, this Kobe 5 model offers exceptional responsiveness and lightweight construction. The shoe's low-profile silhouette allows for quick cuts and agile movements, while the durable outsole ensures excellent traction during intense gameplay. With its eye-catching colorway and premium materials, this sneaker is not only a high-performance basketball shoe but also a fashionable statement piece for young Kobe fans.

Us at StockX believe this product is great for aspiring young basketball players who want to emulate Kobe's on-court excellence while showcasing their style off the court.

products.description:
Air Jordan 12 Retro Taxi 2025 GS brings back one of the most iconic Jordan 12 colorways in a form that stays true to its legacy while welcoming a new generation. The Taxi color blocking has always been about contrast and confidence, and it continues to highlight the Jordan 12’s premium structure and performance driven roots. Even in grade school sizing, the shoe carries the same authority and timeless appeal as the original release.

Collectors appreciate this pair because it represents consistency and heritage. The Air Jordan 12’s radiating stitch lines and clean construction feel just as powerful decades later, proving that strong design never fades. It feels like a foundational Jordan release, celebrated not for novelty but for its lasting place in sneaker history.

The Air Jordan 12 Retro Taxi 2025 GS was released on 11/08/2025 with a retail price of $165.
products.name: Jordan 12 Retro Taxi (2025) (GS)

products.description:
The Jordan 4 Retro Red Cement (GS) presents a fusion of colors, textures, shapes, and materials that will make any grade school kid wearing this sneaker the talk of the playground.

The Grade School version of the Jordan 4 Retro Red Cement sports a white mesh upper overlaid with tumbled white leather along with hits of red synthetic with black speckles along the mud guard, eye stays, and heel tab. Black synthetic hits appear as the waffle eye stays and the toe cap, matching the black sock liner and insole. The Jumpman logo appears in red on the tongue and insole and black on the heel as a raised rubber decal. The white foam midsole encapsulates visible Air for ultimate cushioning.

What are sneaker experts enjoy most about this shoe is the rubber outsole with herringbone traction in pods of black, white, and red, accented with a red Jumpman, thus providing traction and echoing the tri-color look of the upper. The Jordan 4 Retro Red Cement (GS) was released on September 9, 2023 for retail price of $150.
products.name: Jordan 4 Retro Red Cement (GS)

products.description:
The UGG Tasman II Slipper Chestnut Kids is footwear sized for kids that can be worn indoors or outdoors, functioning as both a slipper and a shoe.

It features a soft suede upper in a warm chestnut brown colorway with Tasman branding around the cuff. The plush lining and insole are made of UGGpure upcycled wool. This version has a foam footbed and an outsole made from lightweight Treadlite by UGG. Polyester binding constructed from recycled polyester fiber holds the slipper together.

The UGG Tasman II Slipper Chestnut Kids was released on November 16th, 2017, at a retail price of $70.
products.name: UGG Tasman II Slipper Chestnut (Kids)

products.description:
The Air Jordan 1 Mid Ice Blue GS was manufactured in an ice blue colorway for grade-schoolers.

The accenting blacks fill the dominating vamp, leather panels, and Swooshes, which are established by the quarter overlay, the mudguard, and the collar, as the baby blue colorway combination takes center part. In contrast, the tongue and midfoot design feature a very light Off-White undertone, while the midsole and laces opt for a crisp white finish. It also features the wings logo on its collar. The tongue tag, internal lining, and tread underneath the model's opposing end have an arctic-hued finish.

The Air Jordan 1 Mid Ice Blue GS debuted on 22 October 2022. It retailed at $110.
products.name: Jordan 1 Mid Ice Blue (2022) (GS)

products.description:
Dressed in all leather in a classic two-tone color block, this Nike Dunk Low UNC 2021 with Grade School sizing (GS) is available in Grade School size. The upper on the Nike Dunk Low UNC 2021 (GS) is crafted from smooth white leather, with perforations on the toe box to increase airflow around the foot. The shoe's white base is contrasted by University Blue overlays; University Blue is also the color used on the Swoosh, heel, and heel tag, where the Nike brand name is embroidered in white. "Nike" also appears in University Blue on the lightly padded tongue. The sneaker is completed by a white rubber midsole undergirded by a University Blue outsole.

The Nike Dunk Low UNC 2021 (GS) was released in June, 2021, at a retail price of $85.
products.name: Nike Dunk Low UNC (GS)
